{"tid":321418,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【處女測試】驗證3次屈老婆非處女 賤夫逼死18歲新娘","createTime":"2017-07-14T08:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T10:21:32.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3916fd7f8a5fa0abf35a94333951098cd4349a84","tid":321418,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:02:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170714/56954019?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170714%2F56954019%3F&d=6y2elBPmawR5Jnzn0Ov6z6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=57a5c2b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170714%2F56954019%3F&h=1035bbda\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170714/56954019?</a><br />\n<br />\n塔吉克一位18歲新娘雖然三次通過處女測試，但丈夫卻拒絕相信她是處子之身，更堅持娶第二個妻子，她不堪受辱，新婚40天就自殺身亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n18歲的庫爾希德（Rajabbi Khurshed）在家人安排下下嫁素未謀面的24歲丈夫皮洛夫（Zafar Pirov），雖然庫爾希德已通過政府規定的婚前測試，但皮洛夫仍帶庫爾希德另外接受兩次測試。三次測試顯示，庫爾希德是如假包換的處女，不過皮洛夫竟拒絕相信，更堅持娶第二個老婆，更將她逐出家門。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n庫爾希德不堪受辱自殺，皮洛夫還說：「太太黑字白紙寫明她容許我娶第二個老婆，因為我們結婚時她不是處女。」不過庫爾希德死前曾對父母訴苦，稱為此事承受巨大壓力，再也承受不了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n庫爾希德媽媽形容女兒乖巧，甘願放棄學業去協助照顧兩位殘障的兄弟，她堅持女兒從未有過男友，在婚前亦未曾與任何人做愛。庫爾希德媽媽荒女兒的死感到沮喪，認為她是「誹謗及暴力」的受害人，向總統拉赫蒙（Emomali Rahmon）求助。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n皮洛夫目前被控逼死庫爾希德，一旦罪成，將面臨入獄8年。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170714/large/1500004820_f1ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170714%2Flarge%2F1500004820_f1ae.jpg&h=eeac3c9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4d47e6b981e73c1b44204f20fbdb466886d97a9","tid":321418,"uid":83097,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:04:34.000Z","msg":"24歲丈夫皮洛夫<br />\n?<br />\n24定44"},{"pid":"5d0bf12f1defad0fc9a2916bcecaa8423a41ace5","tid":321418,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d711143a98c217e40e3724c3d1906914befbc85a","tid":321418,"uid":36142,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:27:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>24歲丈夫皮洛夫<br />\n?<br />\n24定44</blockquote><br />\n邊度寫44<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1f5849f504c1fb9e46746baf5d43f3d297723d","tid":321418,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:28:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>24歲丈夫皮洛夫<br />\n?<br />\n24定44</blockquote><br />\n邊度寫44<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驗眼啦 咁既樣24<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add16cd36d1daf16530bbbc3cc29b75531a64307","tid":321418,"uid":50882,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:49:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>24歲丈夫皮洛夫<br />\n?<br />\n24定44</blockquote><br />\n邊度寫44<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驗眼啦 咁既樣24<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咩問題 我都係咁"},{"pid":"3905cf91de014e81bca882b891cd1f76927439f7","tid":321418,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T09:05:23.000Z","msg":"Mustang<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d80ca933d3e0cdd1b5e208f1982350c94f1b2b6","tid":321418,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:21:32.000Z","msg":"可能前面係後面唔係"}]}